18:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Lingvanex and Translated share a solid foundation of core features including Machine Translation, Api Access, File Formats. Where Lingvanex pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Real Time, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Translated uniquely offers Translation Memory and Glossary and Team Collaboration and Quality Assurance and Cms Integration and Custom Models, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Lingvanex holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Translated scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
19:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Lingvanex and Translated offer flexible pricing models. Lingvanex has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Translated does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
